ocs implement on nodejs.

ocs-nodejs 
|--index.js	--  begining
|--service	--  all services defined
|--test		--  demo server, can split to several servers(js) for testing
		 	for example, comment.js, content..
		    curl_command, the way to test the server.

POST:
 curl --data "name=dliang&homepage=initlove" http://localhost:3000/comment/search?test
GET:
 curl http://localhost:3000/user/dliang
